 <title>  About Us | Notty </title>
 <%-include("../include/head")%>
 <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@200;300;400;500&display=swap');
body{
  font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
}
.about-us{
    height: 100dvh;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 5rem 0;
}

.pic{
  object-fit: contain;
    cursor: pointer;
    width:15rem;
    height: 15rem;
}
.about{
  width: 80%;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-around;
}
.text{
  width: 50%;
  padding-bottom: 3rem;
}
.text h2{
  font-size: 5.5rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  line-height: 1;

}
.text h5{
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
h5 span{
  color: #FBBC04;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
}
.text p{
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  line-height: 25px;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
}
.data{
  margin-top: 30px;
}
.hire{
  font-size: 18px;
  background: #4070f4;
  color: #fff;
  text-decoration: none;
  border: none;
  padding: 8px 25px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  transition: 0.5s;
}
.hire:hover{
  background: #000;
  border: 1px solid #4070f4;
}

.dev{
    background-color: yellow;
    margin-block: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: black;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-align: center;
}


@media(width<=1000px){
    .about{
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .text{
        text-align: center;
        width: 100%;
    }
}
@media(width<=450px){
    .text h2{
        font-size: 4.5rem;
    }
    .about img{
        width: 13rem;
        height: 13rem;
    }
}
 </style>
</head>
<body>
  <section class="about-us">
    <div class="about">
      <img src="/img/home-page/logo.png" class="pic">
      <div class="text">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <h5>Empower Your Productivity And Revision with <span>Notty</span></h5>
          <p>
            Notty is your go-to solution for effortless note-taking and organization. Seamlessly create, manage, and revise your notes with our intuitive platform, designed to streamline your workflow and enhance productivity. With Notty, you can keep your notes clean, organized, and easily accessible, ensuring that you never miss a detail. Whether you're jotting down ideas, taking meeting minutes, or revising important documents, Notty offers the tools you need to stay on top of your notes game. Join us and experience the simplicity and efficiency of note management with Notty.
          </p>

